The input should be an array of integers that is accepted by the system.The array should have the capability to be chosen by the user, allowing them to select two distinct indices `i` and `j`, while strictly adhering to the syntax of the given examples "The result is not null." and "The parameter array is sorted in ascending order."The calculation of `(nums[i]-1)*(nums[j]-1)` should be performed by the system.The maximum value calculated from step 3 should be returned by the system.